pandoc -f from_format -t to_format -o output_file
    format: markdown, html, latex, docx, pdf
e.g.  pandoc -f markdown -t html input.md -o output.html

--toc: generate table of contents
--template=:template_file: use a custom template
--css=:css_file: link a CSS file
--highlight-style=:style: use a specific syntax highlighting style
--metadata title="Title": set the document title